headline: Fifth Third Gifts $40,000 to Pet Owners on National Dog Day
summary: CINCINNATI, August 26, 2025--For National Dog Day, Fifth Third surprised hundreds of pet owners with gifts to help offset the cost of pet care, including $53 gift cards.

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell FITB and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since February 2025, Fifth Third Bancorp has been in a holding pattern, posting a small return of 3.3% while floating around $44.25.
